org.encog.examples.neural.cpn

Class RocketCPN

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.encog.examples.neural.cpn.RocketCPN

  • public class RocketCPN
extends Object
    Use a counterpropagation network to determine the angle a rocket is pointed. This is based on a an example by Karsten Kutza, written in C on 1996-01-24. http://www.neural-networks-at-your-fingertips.com
